item.title: CVE-2021-24176|2024-08-03T19:21:18.783Z -- unknown -- jh%20404%20logger
item.description: The JH 404 Logger WordPress plugin through 1.1 doesn't sanitise the referer and path of 404 pages, when they are output in the dashboard, which leads to executing arbitrary JavaScript code in the WordPress dashboard.
